snippet.title: Johnny Depp Speaking on Amber Heard Losing the Case!
snippet.description:
►Johnny Depp Speaking on Amber Heard Losing the Case! 
Johnny Depp supporters mobilize again in the social media for revenge in the face of Johnny following a big reverse in his continuing court struggle against former wife Amber Heard and the British newspaper the Sun. Meanwhile, Amber Heard Johnny shady on Instagram and the fans are completely angry. But does that mean, after all, that Johnny can't prove his guilt?

In April 2018, the Sun published the now infamous column written by the tabloid executive editor Dan Wooten under the headline Gone Potty In his column, Wooten slammed Jk Rowling's decision to keep Johnny in the film and accused the author of being blinded by a personal friendship with the actor.
